## Test Coverage Requirements

| Requirement Type | Test Types Required | Location |
|----|----|-----|
| Functional | Unit Tests, Integration Tests | `tests/unit/`, `tests/integration/` |
| Visual | Visual Regression Tests, Theme Tests | `tests/visual/`, `tests/theme/` |
| Data | Database Tests, API Tests | `tests/integration/`, `tests/api/` |
| Performance | Load Tests, Speed Tests | `tests/performance/` |
| Compatibility | Browser Tests, Device Tests | `tests/compatibility/` |

## Implementation Tasks
- [ ] Write unit tests for all functionality
- [ ] Create Behat scenarios for acceptance criteria
- [ ] Implement visual tests for UI requirements (if applicable)
- [ ] Implement theme tests for theme requirements (if applicable)
- [ ] Implement plugin functionality tests (if applicable)
- [ ] Implement environment compatibility tests (if applicable)
- [ ] Implement feature to pass all tests
- [ ] Measure and ensure code coverage meets 80% threshold
