- [ ] [Task 2]
- [ ] [Task 3]

## Definition of Done
- Tests were written before implementation code
- All tests are passing (unit, integration, visual, theme, etc.)
- Code coverage is at least 80%
- Behat scenarios exist for all acceptance criteria
- All test types applicable to this user story are implemented and passing
- All tests are included in the automated test suite
